{"tid":628884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普傳有私生女 男子收「掩口費」","createTime":"2018-04-14T09:07:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-21T03:57:29.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"a9308ad04a81bdc66ff4f08669f9e7982696aa01","tid":628884,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T09:07:47.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】（星島日報報道）美國總統特朗普的風流史沒完沒了，繼早前有多名女子包括成人片女星聲稱與他有染並獲支付「掩口費」後，一名曾在紐約市特朗普大樓內擔任門房的男子，聲稱掌握黑材料，指特朗普「搭上」他的女管家，兩人有性關係，還誕下了一名私生女。屈指一算，該名私生女現已二十九歲。<br />\n<br />\n該名男子於二○一五年底收取了小報《國民問詢報》三萬美元（約二十三萬四千港元），把這件事保密，以維護特朗普翌年的大選。該名前任門房名叫薩尤丁（Dino Sajudin），他於周四下午發表聲明，承認曾經收受《國民問詢報》的母公司American Media Inc.三萬美元作為「掩口費」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E5%82%B3%E6%9C%89%E7%A7%81%E7%94%9F%E5%A5%B3-%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E6%94%B6-%E6%8E%A9%E5%8F%A3%E8%B2%BB-221122173.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%2582%25B3%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25A7%2581%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%25A5%25B3-%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%2594%25B6-%25E6%258E%25A9%25E5%258F%25A3%25E8%25B2%25BB-221122173.html&d=as0WiOeuhvz8opnM8qFyTwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=d96bda29\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E5%82%B3%E6%9C%89%E7%A7%81%E7%94%9F%E5%A5%B3-%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E6%94%B6-%E6%8E%A9%E5%8F%A3%E8%B2%BB-221122173.html</a>"},{"pid":"18e9f6bfa63e7c17496521708a76809c949dce87","tid":628884,"uid":14103,"like":101,"dislike":0,"score":101,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T09:08:34.000Z","msg":"收左掩口費仲爆出黎咁仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7e6475fba267480bb3f285c9151a393739a12a2","tid":628884,"uid":11962,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"18e9f6bfa63e7c17496521708a76809c949dce87","tid":628884,"uid":14103,"like":101,"dislike":0,"score":101,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T09:08:34.000Z","msg":"收左掩口費仲爆出黎咁仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma